videos.description: Trent Forrest throws the lob to Devin Vassell for the two-handed jam hyping up the Florida State crowd.

videos.headline: Vassell's alley-oop dunk gets the FSU crowd on their feet

videos.description: Trent Forrest goes up top to Dominik Olejniczak for the two-handed jam over the defender.
